Welcome to my personal blog, in order to do spesific task, run this following command

`make html`: build the html, good for production env
`bash ./run-theme.sh`: if you want debug theme, or other stuff under `./submodule/piccolo_theme`
`bash ./run-live.sh`: watch your blog changes

deploying

run this following command
- git submodule update
- python -m venv venv
- ./venv/bin/pip install -r requirements.txt

